POEx-Inotify2 version 0.01
==========================

POEx::Inotify2 - Monitors a directory for events using POE and Linux::Inotify2

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Linux::Inotify2
  POE

